pull_request.title: Manually remove fips202 files left by copy_from_upstream
pull_request.body:
Manually remove some files that should have been removed by copy_from_upstream.

The issue is that copy from upstream does:
`for x in upstream/scheme: copy x to liboqs/scheme`.
But this doesn't handle upstream deletions. It should completely remove liboqs/scheme first.
